<div class='panel'><p>Welcome to the Vulpine Club! We hope you'll enjoy your stay here, and that you'll have lots of interesting discussions and learn about the really neat people around the fediverse. This is a unique and exciting network, and we're pleased you're joining us. Please read the rest of this page to make sure you know what this is all about, and how to play within the rules.</p>

<p><em>Guiding Principle</em>: The Vulpine Club believes strongly in civility and respectfulness as a cornerstone of any online community. Be excellent to each other.</p>

<p><em>Keeping the Lights On</em>: We have a <a href="https://www.patreon.com/vulpineclub">Patreon</a> to help cover the costs of running this thing.  Feel free to chip in as little or as much as you'd like. &lt;3</p>

<p>Special thanks to our sustaining supporters: <a href="/@irick">Irick üêÅüêà‚ö©</a> and (anonymous)!  THANK YOU ALWAYS!</p>

